import reactLogo from '../assets/Skills logo/react.svg'
import expressLogo from '../assets/Skills logo/express.svg'
import reduxLogo from '../assets/Skills logo/redux.svg'
import mongoDBLogo from '../assets/Skills logo/mongodb.svg'
import awsLogo from '../assets/Skills logo/aws.svg'
import tailwindLogo from '../assets/Skills logo/tailwind.svg'

export const skillsData = [
    {
        skill: "ReactJS",
        description: "Leveraging ReactJS to build reusable components",
        key: 1,
        logo: reactLogo
    },
    {
        skill: "Redux",
        description: "Leveraging Redux to efficiently manage state across components in a React app.",
        key: 2,
        logo: reduxLogo
    },
    {
        skill: "ExpressJS",
        description: "Experienced in developing backend APIs using ExpressJS, ensuring efficient data handling and smooth server-side operations.",
        key: 3,
        logo: expressLogo
    },
    {
        skill: "TailwindCSS",
        description: "Adept at utilizing TailwindCSS to design and style modern, intuitive, and visually appealing user interfaces.",
        key: 4,
        logo: tailwindLogo
    },
    {
        skill: "AWS",
        key: 5,
        description: "Knowledgeable in deploying and managing applications on AWS, ensuring scalability, security, and high-performance cloud solutions.",
        logo: awsLogo
    },
]
